<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kawanishi Kaban — Shoot Scripts · Day 1</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #faf8f5;
    --surface: #f0ece6;
    --surface2: #e8e3db;
    --border: #ddd8d0;
    --accent: #9a6e32;
    --accent2: #2e7a8c;
    --accent3: #a04040;
    --text: #1c1a17;
    --muted: #7a7468;
    --cam: #9a6e32;
    --vo: #2e7a8c;
    --shot: #4a7a32;
    --cta: #8c2e6a;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding: 0 0 80px 0;
  }

  /* STICKY HEADER */
  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(250,248,245,0.96);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .site-header .brand {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .site-header .day-tag {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  /* NAV PILLS */
  .nav-scroll {
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .nav-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .nav-pill {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .nav-pill:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* INTRO BANNER */
  .intro {
    padding: 32px 20px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .intro h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .intro h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
  .intro p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .meta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .meta-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .meta-tag.platform { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .meta-tag.style { border-color: var(--accent2); color: var(--accent2); }

  /* EPISODE CARD */
  .episode {
    margin: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }

  .ep-header {
    padding: 24px 20px 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .ep-header:hover { background: #edeae4; }

  .ep-number {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .ep-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .ep-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .ep-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .badge-cam { background: rgba(154,110,50,0.10); color: var(--cam); border: 1px solid rgba(154,110,50,0.25); }
  .badge-vo  { background: rgba(46,122,140,0.10); color: var(--vo);  border: 1px solid rgba(46,122,140,0.25); }
  .badge-solo { background: rgba(74,122,50,0.10); color: var(--shot); border: 1px solid rgba(74,122,50,0.25); }

  .ep-toggle {
    position: absolute;
    right: 20px;
    top: 28px;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .ep-header { position: relative; }
  .episode.open .ep-toggle { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  /* SCRIPT BODY */
  .ep-body {
    display: none;
    padding: 0 20px 28px;
  }
  .episode.open .ep-body { display: block; }

  /* SCENE BLOCKS */
  .scene {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--border);
    padding-left: 16px;
  }
  .scene.cam-scene { border-color: var(--cam); }
  .scene.vo-scene  { border-color: var(--vo);  }
  .scene.shot-scene { border-color: var(--shot); }
  .scene.cta-scene { border-color: var(--cta); }

  .scene-label {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .scene-label.cam  { color: var(--cam); }
  .scene-label.vo   { color: var(--vo);  }
  .scene-label.shot { color: var(--shot); }
  .scene-label.cta  { color: var(--cta); }

  .scene-label .icon { font-size: 13px; }

  .scene-subtitle {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* SPOKEN LINES */
  .lines {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .lines p {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .lines .beat {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 4px 0;
  }
  .lines .emphasis {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* SHOT DIRECTION */
  .shot-dir {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--shot);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .shot-dir p { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* CTA BLOCK */
  .cta-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .cta-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .cta-platform {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cta);
    min-width: 90px;
    padding-top: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cta-line {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* SHOOT NOTE */
  .shoot-note {
    margin-top: 16px;
    background: #f0ece6;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }
  .shoot-note-label {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .shoot-note ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .shoot-note ul li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .shoot-note ul li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .scene-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  /* PROGRESS */
  .progress-bar {
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 200;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.1s;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress"></div></div>

<header class="site-header">
  <span class="brand">Kawanishi Kaban</span>
  <span class="day-tag">📅 Day 1 · Apr 12 · 9 Episodes</span>
</header>

<nav class="nav-scroll">
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep1">Ep 1</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep7">Ep 7</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep8">Ep 8</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep14">Ep 14</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep18">Ep 18</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep23">Ep 23</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep25">Ep 25</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep29">Ep 29</a>
  <a class="nav-pill" href="#ep31">Ep 31</a>
</nav>

<div class="intro">
  <h1>Shoot Scripts<br><span>Day 1 — Talking Heads</span></h1>
  <p>All on-camera episodes. Set up once, run through all 9. Prepare your key points the night before so you're not writing on set.</p>
  <div class="meta-row">
    <span class="meta-tag platform">TikTok + YouTube Shorts</span>
    <span class="meta-tag style">Under 60 sec · 30–45 sec ideal</span>
    <span class="meta-tag">Solo shoot</span>
    <span class="meta-tag">Workshop — on-camera corner</span>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ EP 1 -->
<div class="episode open" id="ep1">
  <div class="ep-header" onclick="toggleEp(this)">
    <div class="ep-number">Episode 01 · Day 1 · Discovery</div>
    <div class="ep-title">The Japanese bag brand the rest of the world hasn't found yet</div>
    <div class="ep-meta">
      <span class="ep-badge badge-cam">On Camera</span>
      <span class="ep-badge badge-vo">Voiceover</span>
      <span class="ep-badge badge-solo">Series Opener</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ep-toggle">▾</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ep-body">

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Hook — On Camera · Direct</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"There's a bag brand in Japan that 70,000 people already love —"</p>
        <p>"and almost none of them are outside Japan."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 1 — On Camera · Walking toward camera</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Medium shot. Bag held naturally. Takamatsu ambient sound. No music yet.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"There's a bag brand in Japan with 70,000 subscribers on YouTube —"</p>
        <p>"and almost none of them are outside Japan."</p>
        <p class="beat">[pause — let it land]</p>
        <p>"I've been working here for six months."</p>
        <p>"I'm just now starting to understand why it's this good."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene vo-scene">
      <div class="scene-label vo"><span class="icon">🎙</span> Scene 2 — Voiceover · Product detail shots</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Slow pan across abb exterior → handle close-up. Music in low.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"The brand is called Kawanishi Kaban."</p>
        <p>"Based in Kagawa — the smallest prefecture in Japan."</p>
        <p>"No visible stitching on the body."</p>
        <p>"Setouchi leather on the handle."</p>
        <p class="beat">[hold on the handle texture — 1 sec]</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 3 — On Camera · Series hook</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"Every day this month I'm going to show you something about this brand that surprised me."</p>
        <p>"Starting with this."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene vo-scene">
      <div class="scene-label vo"><span class="icon">🎙</span> Scene 4 — Voiceover · Macro close-up</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Extreme close-up of abb exterior — find the bonded area, no seam.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"No stitching on the outside."</p>
        <p>"The whole bag is bonded."</p>
        <p class="beat">[hold]</p>
        <p>"That's not normal."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cta-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cta"><span class="icon">📲</span> CTA</div>
      <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="cta-item">
          <span class="cta-platform">TikTok</span>
          <span class="cta-line">"Follow if you want to see what else this brand is hiding."</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-item">
          <span class="cta-platform">YT Shorts</span>
          <span class="cta-line">"Subscribe — tomorrow I'll show you where this brand actually came from."</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="shoot-note">
      <div class="shoot-note-label">📋 Shoot Priorities</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Walk toward camera naturally — not posed, just moving</li>
        <li>Wide Takamatsu shot behind you — not Tokyo</li>
        <li>Slow pan across abb exterior — bonded seam area</li>
        <li>Handle close-up — Setouchi leather texture</li>
        <li>One moment holding bag, no words</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ EP 7 -->
<div class="episode" id="ep7">
  <div class="ep-header" onclick="toggleEp(this)">
    <div class="ep-number">Episode 07 · Day 1 · Reaction</div>
    <div class="ep-title">Western people have some wild assumptions about Japanese bags</div>
    <div class="ep-meta">
      <span class="ep-badge badge-cam">On Camera</span>
      <span class="ep-badge badge-solo">Solo · Casual</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ep-toggle">▾</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ep-body">

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Hook — On Camera · Direct</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Prepare 3–4 real comments or Reddit posts in advance. Have them on your phone.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"I've been reading what people outside Japan actually think about Japanese bag brands."</p>
        <p class="beat">[beat]</p>
        <p>"Some of these comments are wild."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 1 — React to Comment 1</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Read or show the comment. React naturally. Don't over-perform.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"Okay so someone said: <span class="emphasis">[read comment]</span>"</p>
        <p class="beat">[genuine reaction — short, real]</p>
        <p>"Here's what's actually true:"</p>
        <p>"<span class="emphasis">[correct it in 1–2 sentences]</span>"</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 2 — React to Comment 2</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"This one actually made me laugh —"</p>
        <p>"<span class="emphasis">[read comment]</span>"</p>
        <p class="beat">[beat]</p>
        <p>"<span class="emphasis">[real honest reaction]</span>"</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 3 — Closer</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"I had the same assumptions before I moved here."</p>
        <p>"Being inside the workshop kind of changed all of that."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cta-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cta"><span class="icon">📲</span> CTA</div>
      <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="cta-item">
          <span class="cta-platform">TikTok</span>
          <span class="cta-line">"Drop your assumption in the comments — I'll tell you if it's true."</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-item">
          <span class="cta-platform">YT Shorts</span>
          <span class="cta-line">"What do you think Japanese bags actually cost? Guess in the comments."</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="shoot-note">
      <div class="shoot-note-label">📋 Prep Before Shoot</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Find 3–4 real Reddit/TikTok comments about Japanese bag brands tonight</li>
        <li>Pick ones that are wrong in an interesting way — not mean, just genuinely mistaken</li>
        <li>No props needed. Casual setup. Energy slightly playful, not defensive.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ EP 8 -->
<div class="episode" id="ep8">
  <div class="ep-header" onclick="toggleEp(this)">
    <div class="ep-number">Episode 08 · Day 1 · Discovery</div>
    <div class="ep-title">What I noticed after one week of daily use</div>
    <div class="ep-meta">
      <span class="ep-badge badge-cam">On Camera</span>
      <span class="ep-badge badge-solo">Honest · Personal</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ep-toggle">▾</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ep-body">

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Hook — On Camera</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"I've been using this bag every day for a week."</p>
        <p>"A few things I didn't expect."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 1 — Observation 1</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Hold abb naturally. Don't look at it too much — talk from experience.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"The handle."</p>
        <p>"I didn't think it would matter which leather they used there."</p>
        <p>"But after a week of holding it in summer heat —"</p>
        <p>"it actually feels different. Better. Less slippery."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 2 — Observation 2</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"The weight."</p>
        <p>"I thought it'd be heavier for how solid it feels."</p>
        <p>"It's not. It sits well."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 3 — Honest Observation</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"One thing I'm still figuring out —"</p>
        <p>"<span class="emphasis">[add your own genuine observation here]</span>"</p>
        <p class="beat">[this keeps it real, not promotional]</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cta-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cta"><span class="icon">📲</span> CTA</div>
      <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="cta-item">
          <span class="cta-platform">Both</span>
          <span class="cta-line">"I'll keep updating this as I use it longer. Follow if you want to see how it holds up."</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="shoot-note">
      <div class="shoot-note-label">📋 Shoot Notes</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Use abb as the hero bag — hold it, don't set it on a table</li>
        <li>Tone: relaxed, honest — like talking to a friend, not reviewing a product</li>
        <li>Fill in Scene 3 with something real you've actually noticed</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ EP 14 -->
<div class="episode" id="ep14">
  <div class="ep-header" onclick="toggleEp(this)">
    <div class="ep-number">Episode 14 · Day 1 · Discovery</div>
    <div class="ep-title">The thing foreigners always ask me about this bag</div>
    <div class="ep-meta">
      <span class="ep-badge badge-cam">On Camera</span>
      <span class="ep-badge badge-solo">Conversational</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ep-toggle">▾</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ep-body">

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Hook — On Camera</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"Every time I have this bag outside the workshop —"</p>
        <p>"someone asks me the same question."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 1 — The Question</div>
      <div class="scene-subtitle">Pick one: price / where to buy / brand name / why it looks different. Choose the most real one.</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"They ask: <span class="emphasis">'How much is it?'</span>"</p>
        <p class="beat">[or whatever the real question is]</p>
        <p>"And honestly — my answer surprises them."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cam-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cam"><span class="icon">🎬</span> Scene 2 — The Answer</div>
      <div class="lines">
        <p>"It's not cheap. But it's not what you'd expect for what you're getting."</p>
        <p>"These bags are made to last — like, repair-for-life kind of made."</p>
        <p>"When I explain that, people usually stop asking about the price."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene cta-scene">
      <div class="scene-label cta"><span class="icon">📲</span> CTA</div>
      <div class="cta-block">
        <div class="cta-item">
          <span class="cta-platform">Both</span>
          <span class="cta-line">"What would your first question be? Drop it below."</span>
